Below is a concrete mapping system + UI layout you can actually build.

1️⃣ Core idea for Hyper 3D
Goal:
One shared 3D universe view (React Three Fiber + Three.js) where each repo is a planet, and the planet’s appearance + motion are calculated from live data and quests. React Three Fiber lets you build Three.js scenes as React components, perfect for wiring them straight to your existing React state.

2D Hub = calm command centre (you already shipped this).

Hyper 3D = visual skin over the same data, not a separate logic system.

Everything animates from the data, not random.

